From: " (USANYS)" 
To: "-(USANYS)" 
Subject: Memo for AUSA 
Date: Fri, 16 Oct 2020 16:14:52 +0000 
Attachments: -_Meino.pdf 
Inline-Images: image001.png 
Urgent. Please send the below email and the attachment back to me. 
The SDNY requests approval for travel by AUSA to the U.K. from October 12 to October 17, 2020. This travel is 
required at this time as will be conducting an interview of victim/witness in the case against Ghislaine Maxwell. 
The victim was a victim of Jeffrey Epstein. She will only talk to us person and it is necessary for us to get her statement on 
the record to preserve the government's right to use her at trial. 
Please issue an approval from EOUSA for her travel to the U.K. 
Acting United States Attorney. 
EFTA00015642
